// Cespenar
@6800 = ~Fun bumping into you here.~
@6801 = ~How come you are here?~  // Player
@6802 = ~I did not expect to see you again.~  // Player
@6803 = ~I see you are serving the enemy now.~  // Player
@6804 = ~Back home and back to work for rattlebones over there. See, I have my work bench!~
@6805 = ~Oh, is pyroclastic dragon scales. It hurts touching! I make good plate armor, though...ouch... gotsa be careful. 10,000 gp... you wants?~
@6806 = ~Kinda happy you said no...those scales hurt to touch!~

// Uthaedeol & Culdus 
@6900 = ~Traitor! You should suffer a thousand deaths for betraying Bhaal.~ [mobha112] 
@6901 = ~Blood-drenched?! You are supposed to be in stasis!~  [mobha111] // Culdus
@6902 = ~Were you so lucky. I am very much awake and will avenge my lord Bhaal. Die like the pathetic maggot you are.~ [mobha113] 
@6903 = ~With them out of the way, it is only us and Amelyssan. Sadly, my lord Bhaal remains dead regardless of what happens next.~ [mobha114] 
@6904 = ~Your capabilities are impressive, but I would prefer to make the attempt at divinity for myself.~ [mobha115] 
@6905 = ~Reconsider, I can promise you great rewards once we see this through.~  // Player
@6906 = ~I should have expected as much from a servant of Bhaal.~  // Player
@6907 = ~Good, I've been looking forward to gutting you!~  // Player

// Viekang (Sal - Pleading)
@7000 = ~Given your reputation, I would rather be left with the Solar.~ //[mobha180] 
@7001 = ~You're a sight for sore eyes. You couldn't have arrived quickly enough.~ //[mobha181] 
@7002 = ~As I was escaping Saradush, the Planetar must have sensed me. They swooped in out of nowhere and all quickly faded to black.~ //[mobha182] 
@7003 = ~I don't know how long I was out for, but I awaken here to be tortured and experimented on by this twisted Solar. He even has me bound to chains that prevent me from teleporting away.~ //[mobha183]
@7004 = ~Please, I beg of you, set me free from this place. I barely have any of Bhaal's essence to matter.~ //[mobha184]
@7005 = ~I will set you free at once, flee this place.~  // Player 1
@7006 = ~Swear an oath to me to never attempt to rise up and take the mantle of our father. In this place an oath will have power, like a geas. I will then give you your freedom.~  // Player 1
@7007 = ~Little or not, I cannot have any loose ends running around. It's nothing personal, but you have to die.~  // Player 1
@7008 = ~Die like the trapped animal that you are.~  // Player 1
@7009 = ~I need a moment to think on this.~  // Player 1
@7010 = ~Please, don't think on it for too long!~ //[mobha185]
@7011 = ~Coward! I hope Amelyssan kills you!~ //[mobha186]
@7012 = ~I swear. I will swear it here. You have my oath I will not try to become the Lord of Murder.~ //[mobha187]
@7013 = ~No offense, but I hope this is the last time I see you. Good luck against Amelyssan.~ //[mobha188]
@7014 = ~I can't risk it. Die, fool!~  // Player 1

// Jambi (Eleven Labs Giovanni) - OLD (Jean-Pierre - Arrogant)
@7100 = ~Please, see what I have to offer.~ [mobha232]//[mobha200]
@7101 = ~Yes~
@7102 = ~No~
@7103 = ~Good day, and thanks for stopping by.~ [mobha233]//[mobha193]

@7110 = ~Welcome! It is not everyday we see a Prime walk into our sanctuary.~ [mobha231]//[mobha192]
@7111 = ~We are an odd accompaniment of assorted beings, but all are welcome.~ [mobha234]//[mobha196]
@7112 = ~What is this place?~  // Player1
@7113 = ~Who are you?~  // Player 1
@7114 = ~Why is your sanctuary out here?~  // Player 1
@7115 = ~I have no desire to speak with you.~  // Player 1
@7116 = ~Why of course. I am a merchant and innkeep, so please feel free to speak with me if you are in need of my services.~ [mobha235]//[mobha194]
@7117 = ~You'd refer to my kind as "Mercane". Like most of my people, I am a merchant and happy to trade and do business with you.~ [mobha236]//[mobha195]
@7118 = ~I also manage an inn. It isn't much, but it will be a safe place for you to rest.~ [mobha237]//[mobha197]
@7119 = ~Are there any services of interest to you?~ [mobha238]//[mobha198]
@7120 = ~Good question! I would refer you to Malik to better assist you. We do not have a leader here, but he is our representative in dealing with matters concerning the community.~ [mobha239]//[mobha199]
@7121 = ~I need a safe place to lay my head.~  // Player 1
@7122 = ~Let me see your store.~  // Player 1
@7123 = ~I'm good for now.~  // Player 1

// Kirinhale (Lilith - Seductive)
@7200 = ~Who are you to be in a place such as this?~ [mobha253]
@7201 = ~Wait, you look familiar. Have we crossed paths before?~ [mobha254]
@7202 = ~I set you free in Durlag's Tower.~  // Player 1
@7203 = ~We met in Durlag's Tower, and I left you to rot.~  // Player 1
@7204 = ~I killed you in Durlag's Tower.~  // Player 1
@7205 = ~No, I don't think we have.~  // Player 1
@7206 = ~The irony. When we parted I said your type is destined to meet mine, yet here we are again face to face.~ [mobha255]
@7207 = ~You have little reason to trust me as I've already failed to honor past bargains we've made, but do hear me out.~ [mobha256]
@7208 = ~That's right, I remember you. Lucky for me another fool adventuring party came in shortly after you cleared the Tower. They took me up on my deal, and I managed to escape.~ [mobha257]
@7209 = ~Most unfortunate that was, but it did grant me my freedom in the end. I'm willing to put that behind us if you hear me out.~ [mobha258]
@7210 = ~Perhaps I've been in the Abyss too long, I don't frequently mistake a face.~ [mobha259]
@7211 = ~As punishment for my absence due to Durlag's imprisonment, I must atone by providing a great many souls to my master.~ [mobha260]
@7212 = ~What better place to harvest souls than those belonging unattended to a dead god?~ [mobha261]
@7213 = ~I feel a thin veil here where they will be ripe for the taking. However, despite being dead, Bhaal has enacted safeguards to keep his souls safe from thieves, such as me.~ [mobha262]
@7214 = ~It is within my power to give you delights unearthly if you assist me in this manner.~  [mobha263]// MALE PC
@7215 = ~If you want to help a fellow vixen atone, I could use your aid.~  [mobha264]// FEMALE PC
@7216 = ~I don't know why, but I suspect you are attempting to get into Bhaal's realm. I don't have much time, so I'll even give you this medallion I found off one of his followers. It should allow you to bypass the protective warding.~ [mobha265]
@7217 = ~I see I don't have a choice in the matter. I'll aid you.~  // Player 1
@7218 = ~As the souls are of a foul nature, I will help you.~  // Player 1
@7219 = ~What do you plan on using the souls for?~  // Player 1
@7220 = ~Evil souls or not, I cannot allow you to do this.~  // Player 1
@7221 = ~I plan on becoming the new Lord of Murder and won't allow you to pre-emptively steal from me.~  // Player 1
@7222 = ~Same as any would do in the Abyss. Both devils and demons harvest souls as yet more fodder for the eternal blood war.~ [mobha266]
@7223 = ~Worthless mortal! I will go elsewhere to hunt for souls.~ [mobha267]
@7224 = ~Splendid! Prepare yourself, I suspect we will be attacked as soon as I begin the attempt.~ [mobha268]
@7225 = ~With that unpleasantry out of the way, I will quickly pierce the vale to collect my souls and return in short order.~ [mobha269]
@7226 = ~And it is done! As promised, here is Bhaal's Medallion.~ [mobha270]
@7227 = ~As for the unearthly delights, I have no intention of honoring that bargain. I have places to be, male, and will waste no more time on this Plane.~ [mobha271]
@7228 = ~I have places to be and souls to deliver. Perhaps our paths will cross again.~ [mobha272]

// Jambi - Rescue (Eleven Labs Giovanni) 
@7300 = ~Blessings to you! You saved me from the dragon!~ [mobha245]
@7301 = ~I was traveling through the area and was beset by that creature. Without your intervention, I fear my demise would have been most swift and painful.~ [mobha246]
@7302 = ~Who are you?~  // Player 1
@7303 = ~What is this place?~  // Player 1
@7304 = ~I have no desire to speak with you.~  // Player 1
@7305 = ~Of course! Please take this necklace as a token of my appreciation. I am a merchant, so feel free to speak with me if you are interested in trade.~ [mobha247]
@7306 = ~Good day, and thanks for stopping by.~ [mobha233]
@7307 = ~We are in Khalas which is the first layer of the Outer Plane known as Gehenna.~ [mobha249]
@7308 = ~You'd refer to my kind as "Mercane". Like most of my people, I am a merchant and happy to trade and do business with you.~ [mobha236]
@7309 = ~Do you wish to trade?~ [mobha248]
@7310 = ~Please, see what I have to offer.~ [mobha232]
@7311 = ~Let me see your store.~  // Player 1
@7312 = ~I'm good for now.~  // Player 1
@7313 = ~Please, take this necklace as a token of my appreciation.~ [mobha250]
@7314 = ~Of course! I am a merchant, so feel free to speak with me if you are interested in trade.~ [mobha251]
@7315 = ~Greetings! I am Jambi, a traveling merchant making my way through this most inhospitable Plane.~ [mobha252]
@7316 = ~A traveling merchant? I'd like to see your wares.~  // Player 1
@7317 = ~Why are you traveling here? I can't imagine you'd find many customers in these parts.~  // Player 1
@7318 = ~You are certainly correct, and I don't like spending more time here than I have to.~ [mobha273]
@7319 = ~Khalas is a necessary pathway as this is the only layer of Gehenna that touches the Astral Plane and has connections to the planes of Hades, Baator, and the Concordant Opposition.~ [mobha274]
@7320 = ~As a neutral merchant, I can ply my trade across the denizens of these realms.~ [mobha275]

// Noober (Elevenlabs Callum) - OLD (Atlas - Light-hearted)
@7400 = ~Hi, I'm Noober. Nice place, huh?~
@7401 = ~What...~  // Player 1
@7402 = ~How...~  // Player 1
@7403 = ~Who...~  // Player 1
@7404 = ~It is time to reveal my true face.~
@7405 = ~Greetings. I am Ao, the Overfather.~ [mobha221]//[mobha202]
@7406 = ~You look surprised? Cyric was correct in his meeting with you, and I have watched your progress with interest. Noober, and his various offshoots, were a cloak allowing me to observe and interact with you on your journey, without drawing undue attention to myself.~ [mobha222]//[mobha203]
@7407 = ~How could you not help me?~  // Player 1
@7408 = ~Why did you not make your presence known?~  // Player 1
@7409 = ~And rob you of the chance to prove yourself?~ [mobha223]//[mobha205]
@7410 = ~This journey is your crucible. As steel is forged under the hottest flames, so too you have been strengthened by the adversity you faced. What would you have done in the absence of such challenges? Continued your existence in Candlekeep? You would have wasted your life away and never developed into who you are today.~ [mobha224]//[mobha204]
@7411 = ~Tymora, Lady Luck, picked up an interest in you and provided aid early in your journey. Such things like diamonds in trees, magical rings in rocks, and so on. After the ankheg plate in Nashkel, I had to intervene. You piqued my interest then, and Noober was born.~ [mobha225]//[mobha206]
@7412 = ~Why are you revealing yourself to me now?~  // Player 1
@7413 = ~This has been a most interesting series of events, and little of mortal affairs has caught my attention quite like this. Of course I wanted the opportunity to present myself at the end.~ [mobha226]//[mobha207]
@7414 = ~Will you assist me in defeating Amelyssan?~  // Player 1
@7415 = ~My life is not a plaything for greater beings.~  // Player 1
@7416 = ~I don't want this. Remove my divine blood and make me a mortal, so I can walk away from this.~  // Player 1
@7417 = ~You have the power, make me a god here and now. Crush Amelyssan!~  // Player 1
@7418 = ~No. What comes next is for you to face.~ [mobha227]//[mobha208]
@7419 = ~I shall neither provide support nor oppose your ascension. You must succeed on your own merit, skill, and ability. The pantheon of gods is diverse and covers both good and evil. All have their place and purpose.~ [mobha228]//[mobha209]
@7420 = ~I will leave you with this, Bhaal's throne holds a lever that will open the way to the Mana Forge. It is within the Mana Forge where Bhaal's essence is collected and where Amelyssan awaits you. Whomever rises as the victor I will grant godhood, if they so choose.~ [mobha229]//[mobha210]
@7421 = ~The rest is in your hands, and I look forward to the finale.~ [mobha230]//[mobha211]

// Nekri (Casey - Lit)
@7500 = ~Halt traveler!~ [mobha242]
@7501 = ~We are a neutral outpost and all are welcome to enter. Violence will not be tolerated.~ [mobha244]
@7502 = ~You look capable. Please seek Malik as we can use your help.~ [mobha243]

// Malik
@7600 = ~This is placeholder dialog.~